{This game was preceeded by a funny story. Mikenas says: "The evening before I
was having dinner in a restaurant was, unexpectedly, Alekhine approached my
table and sat down. Although he looked in good shape, some nervousness was
apparent, probably due to his defeat in a match against Euwe in 1935 and his
loss of the title of world champion. I invited him for a drink. He refused,
kindly but firmly: - Milk only, please! - he answered. I have to win the world
champion title back, and I will not allow myself any lack of control. - Then
he confessed - If I have lost the title it is because of such damned drinks!.
I congratulated with him for his firm self discipline. For few minutes we
talked about anything, then he greeted me like a good friend with his best
