was sounder, e.g. 9...} 9... h6 10. Bxf6 Qxf6 11. Nbd2 {with an equal game.})
9... Bxf3 10. gxf3 ({If} 10. Qxf3 {then 10...} 10... Nxb4 11. cxb4 Bd4 {
