do the poor? If he would save the Rock by playing 14...Rg8 I should play 15.
Qxh7 Kxf7 16.Rf1+. I had him already in my hands - and his wicked laugh during
his speech freezed my blood - I surely should not let him go. Ha, ha!} 15. Rf1+
Ke8 16. Rxf8+ {"At this point my victim looked at my, in my eyes - said
finally the "murder" - and his lost look, his impotence feeling, his sorrow,
